de.rcblum.stream.deck.items

Class URIItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rcblum.stream.deck.items.AbstractStreamItem
      • de.rcblum.stream.deck.items.URIItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StreamKeyListener, StreamItem

    public class URIItem
extends AbstractStreamItem
    This handle can be registered with the StreamDeck and will browse the given URI when the stream deck button is pressed on release.
